        Selling in Everton Hills 2026
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Everton Hills offers the larger blocks and quieter family streets that have become hard to find closer to the Brisbane CBD. Here is what sellers need to know about pricing, presentation and timing in 2026.
      </p>
